title: NYT: U.S. investigating Cambridge Analytica
text:
NYT: U.S. investigating Cambridge Analytica Wednesday, May 16, 2018 - 00:58
The New York Times reports the U.S. Justice Department and the FBI are investigating Cambridge Analytica, a now-defunct political data firm embroiled in a scandal over its handling of Facebook user information.
